item.description:
@Sleep wrote:

Ah simple fix. When it compiles if there is an error it tells you what that error is. Just go back in your client.java or where the error is accuring from (usually client.java) and delete what it is. But the server will still run and anyone on your server playing with you will not be aware of the fact that you have a tad mishap with your client.
